Date: Fri, 20 Feb 2026 19:32:31 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 41/50] Add an autofix for the Slowness lint

Summary:
I can never remember the syntax for `strncmp`, so have the machine do it for me.

Includes support for `str_contains` and `str_starts_with` if the linter config is set to use PHP 8 or newer.

Test Plan:
* Run unit tests
* (Optional) Write some code using strstr, strchr, strpos that is slow and run this lint

Reviewers: O1 Blessed Committers, avivey

Reviewed By: O1 Blessed Committers, avivey

Subscribers: tobiaswiese, valerio.bozzolan, Matthew, Cigaryno

Differential Revision: https://we.phorge.it/D26778
